    "Huazheng's ESG rating covers 3 first-level indicators, 14 s-level indicators, 26 third-level indicators, and more than 130 bottom-level data indicators.",
    "Compared with the overseas market, it incorporates more indicators suitable for the current development stage in China, such as the quality of information disclosure, CSRC punishment, and targeted poverty alleviationThe bottom indicators are aggregated from bottom to top according to the industry weight matrix to obtain the enterprise's ESG score and the final AAA-C rating of nine grades.",
